## Import Ordering

Imports must follow this order (enforced by ESLint `import/order`):

1. Node built-ins (`path`, `fs`)
2. External packages (`react`, `next/*`, third-party libraries)
3. Internal aliases (`@/lib/*`, `@/components/*`, `@/services/*`)
4. Relative imports (`./UserCard`, `../utils`)
5. Type imports (`import type { ... }`)

```tsx
// Good
import { Suspense } from "react";
import Image from "next/image";
import { useQuery } from "@tanstack/react-query";

import { Button } from "@/components/ui";
import { useUsers } from "@/services/users";

import type { User } from "@/types/user";
```

